# Everything else keeps connect-src TIGHT (no external origins: 'self' + blob: + nano-gpt.com only;
# blob: is local, see note above). play.html runs UNTRUSTED shared apps (arbitrary bundled
# HTML/JS): the tight external gate stops a malicious app from fetch-exfiltrating the viewer's
# inputs or API key to an attacker origin. legal.html is plain content but defaults to the same
# tight policy.
#
# EXCEPTION — /play + /play.html widen connect-src (and ONLY connect-src — never
# img/media/script/frame) to https:, for TWO trusted-parent-chrome features: the opt-in "shorten
# this share link" button (tinyurl.com, da.gd) and output persistence (the parent fetches a
# generated video/music result's bytes off the provider CDN — e.g. *.cloudfront.net, hosts we
# can't enumerate — to store them in IndexedDB before the CDN URL expires; same rationale as the
# editor's connect-src https: for its media "save"). The UNTRUSTED shared app does NOT get any of
# this: it runs in a srcdoc iframe that re-seals its OWN connect-src back to 'self' blob: nano-gpt
# via a <meta> CSP (PREVIEW_CSP in play.html), and the browser enforces every delivered policy by
# intersection — so a malicious app still cannot fetch-exfiltrate viewer inputs/outputs anywhere.
# legal.html stays fully tight.
/play
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://nano-gpt.com; media-src 'self' data: blob: https:; connect-src 'self' blob: https://nano-gpt.com https:; frame-src 'self' blob:; child-src blob:; worker-src 'self' blob:; font-src 'self' data:; base-uri 'none'; form-action 'none'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'self'; upgrade-insecure-requests
/play.html
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://nano-gpt.com; media-src 'self' data: blob: https:; connect-src 'self' blob: https://nano-gpt.com https:; frame-src 'self' blob:; child-src blob:; worker-src 'self' blob:; font-src 'self' data:; base-uri 'none'; form-action 'none'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'self'; upgrade-insecure-requests
/legal
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://nano-gpt.com; media-src 'self' data: blob: https:; connect-src 'self' blob: https://nano-gpt.com; frame-src 'self' blob:; child-src blob:; worker-src 'self' blob:; font-src 'self' data:; base-uri 'none'; form-action 'none'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'self'; upgrade-insecure-requests
/legal.html
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://nano-gpt.com; media-src 'self' data: blob: https:; connect-src 'self' blob: https://nano-gpt.com; frame-src 'self' blob:; child-src blob:; worker-src 'self' blob:; font-src 'self' data:; base-uri 'none'; form-action 'none'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'self'; upgrade-insecure-requests

